use flake

# Run `bazel` inside the rules_tf2-dev container instead of nix's bazel.
# WORKAROUND: nix's bazel isn't compatible with our RBE setup (it leaks
# /nix/store paths into actions a vanilla worker can't reproduce). The shim in
# tools/dev/ shadows the nix bazel; see tools/dev/bazel for the full rationale.
# PATH_add must come AFTER `use flake` so the shim wins over the nix bazel.
PATH_add tools/dev

# Bazel shell completion is wired up by the flake dev-shell's shellHook.